4º should we always work with standertized data? It says that for regression we need to do it but what about the others

só dentro do split é que devemos normalizar, normalizar e centrar os outputs.

para y n é preciso divir pela standart deviation

para X é centrar e dividir pela stnadar

X^train = (X_train-X_mean_train)/X_std_train

X^test = (X_test-X_mean_train)/X_std_train

y^train = y_train-y_mean_train

y^test = y_test-y_mean_train

5º What should we do with the best model for a certain inner fold. Use the mean of the best predictions, becuase we used it to feature selection nt model selection

